i love these movies. i've watched the free ones on Amazon Prime dozens of times. However, none of the movies on this disc are in HD. i knew right away these movies would be grainy because there was only one disc. For all three of these movies to fit in this package in HD, there would have had to have been at least two discs, maybe three. Given the price, slightly over $10 a piece, i expected HD. Maybe that's just me.

It is all the 80s actions movies taking place in the 2010s.  Do not look for sophisticated plot lines or profound reflection.  These are 3 movies of just low expectations, shoot-em-up, action movies.  They are great fun to watch.  Kick back with a beer, pizza/wings and be entertained.
